translated: Federico da Montefeltro, born in Gubbio in 1422, died in Ferrara in 1482, is a condottiere (warlord) of the Renaissance, Duke of Urbino and Montefeltro count of 1444 to his death.
original: Frédéric III de Montefeltro, né à Gubbio en 1422, mort à Ferrare en 1482, est un condottiere (chef de guerre) de la Renaissance, duc d'Urbino et comte de Montefeltro de 1444 à sa mort.
